List activity in a given Databrary session for which the user has ownership privileges.

Source: R/list_session_activity.R
list_session_activity.Rd

List activity in a given Databrary session for which the user has ownership privileges.

Usage

list_session_activity(session_id = 6256, vb = FALSE)

Arguments

session_id

Selected session/slot number.

vb

A Boolean value. If TRUE provides verbose output.

Value

A list with the activity history on a slot.

Examples

list_session_activity()
